The paper discusses the implementation and evaluation of multiple-writer/multiple-reader (MWMR) atomic register algorithms in a distributed system, which involves topics related to distributed computing (cs.DC), distributed systems (cs.DS), network infrastructure (cs.NI), operating systems (cs.OS), and system and control theory (cs.SY).
